com.africanbongo.clearskyes.model

Class WeatherLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.africanbongo.clearskyes.model.WeatherLocation

  • public class WeatherLocation
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that represents the data of a certain geolocation, that is:
    • URL location (used in forming the url to get the location)
    • City
    • Country
    • Country code, eg. ZW or US
    • Region, such as provinces or states

      • getLongStringLocation

        public java.lang.String getLongStringLocation()

        A String representing the information about the location in full.

        If region is returned from api it returns e.g. Harare, Mashonaland West, Zimbabwe

        If region is not returned from api it returns e.g. Harare, Zimbabwe

        Returns:
        String representing the information about location in full.

      • getStandardStringLocation

        If region is not returned from api it returns e.g. Zimbabwe

        Returns:
        String representing the information about location in standard form.
